column5: and uh roadrunner is in midair kind of running
and it says roadrunner and his scientific name
and they show coyote and his scien
yeah with his knife and fork
and um then they start up again
and coyote thinks he’s got him
so he goes to stab him with his knife and fork
and gets like a burst of acceleration
but he ends up stabbing the road underneath him
and his feet are sticking up in the air
and now he’s sitting there thinking
and he comes up with a plan
so he gives a thumbs up
and then he’s got this contraption
with a like a boxing glove fist thing attached to it
and he pulls the spring back
so when the roadrunner comes by
but the glove stays in place
pushes him back into a bould another boulder
and then the glove comes back
and punches him in the head
so now he has a blueprint for a new plan
uh a tightrope in the middle
and he’s gonna walk out on the tightrope with an anvil
step one walk out onto the rope
and he walks out onto the rope
well he gets out to the middle of the rope
and now he’s standing on the ground
and runs back in the other direction
and so he throws his anvil aside
but now the rope is not weighed down anymore
so he goes flying up into the air
and he pulls a string for the parachute
but it’s just his backpack opens
and it’s all stuff’s coming out
um then you see him again chasing the roadrunner
so he starts running into the mine
and you just see like his eyeballs
and um so he runs back to the beginning
and gets one of those hats with like the light on the front
and he’s got a hat too
roadrunner has a hat with a green light
coyote has a hat with a red light
so then they run into the mine
and you just see a top view
with um the green light roadrunner
he’s chasing after the uh roadrunner
and um all of a sudden
the uh roadrunner is kinda gone
and coyote’s light goes out on his hat
and they show you the view
of you know like the ground above him
like the shape of the cactuses kinda blows up
